<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>291</hymn_number>
<title>TUAN ZUNGZAL KO CH291</title>
<key>D</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Maw ka hawile zoh tuah ngiatnak, Vancung ah a lang A kan bawmtu a ra
 te lai, Teinak a nai cang.

[C1]
   &quot;Ka rat than hlan tiang tuan u,&quot; Jesuh a kan chimh, Maw Bawipa kan
   tuan zungzal lai, Na bia kha kan zumh.

[V2]
 Zohhmanh ral tampi an hung lio, Rul-hreu hmai a sa Zaang thawngmi a
 cheu an ril cang, Kan thawnnak a dai.

[C2]
   &quot;Ka rat than hlan tiang tuan u,&quot; Jesuh a kan chimh, Maw Bawipa kan
   tuan zungzal lai, Na bia kha kan zumh.

[V3]
 Zungzal tei ngiatnak kha zoh tuah, Muko thawng kha ngai Hmai a kan
 saktu a min in, Ral kha kan tei lai.

[C3]
   &quot;Ka rat than hlan tiang tuan u,&quot; Jesuh a kan chimh, Maw Bawipa kan
   tuan zungzal lai, Na bia kha kan zumh.

[V4]
 Ral dohnak kha a sau ko i, Bawmhnak a nai cang, Kannih Ralbawi a phan
 deng cang, Lunglawm cio tuah u.

[C4]
   &quot;Ka rat than hlan tiang tuan u,&quot; Jesuh a kan chimh, Maw Bawipa kan
   tuan zungzal lai, Na bia kha kan zumh.</lyrics>
</song>